title: BRIEF-Sensys Gatso says wins order worth SEK 51 million in Australia
text:
Oct 16 Sensys Gatso Group AB
* Sensys Gatso says wins order worth SEK 51 million in Australia
* Says deliveries and installation holds a value of SEK 21 million crowns and the maintenance contract SEK 30 million crowns Further company coverage: (Stockholm Newsroom)
